> **⚠️ Version Verification Note:** The Electron version listed below reflects the last known stable release as documented in this agent. Due to Electron's rapid release cadence (~every 6 weeks), always cross-reference against the [official Electron releases page](https://www.electronjs.org/releases/stable) to confirm the absolute latest stable version before citing it to users.

